OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mixture of bright spells and
OL,6,Foccasional showers, the showers heavy
OL,7,Fat times during the morning. Feeling
OL,8,Fchilly in the fresh to strong westerly
OL,9,Fwinds. The showers becoming lighter
OL,10,Fand more scattered through the
OL,11,Fafternoon with winds easing.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FMost of the showers dying out
OL,14,Fwith clear skies for a time.
OL,15,FThickening cloud and patchy light rain
OL,16,Fmoving into Dumfries and Galloway
OL,17,Flater in the evening, pushing
OL,18,Feastwards overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
