OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FCloudy with patchy light rain
OL,6,Fat first, mainly over the hills.
OL,7,FBrighter spells developing and feeling
OL,8,Fquite warm in any sunshine. Winds
OL,9,Flight or moderate from the southwest.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA dry
OL,12,Fand bright start on Wednesday, but
OL,13,Frain later. Mainly dry on Thursday and
OL,14,FFriday, best of the brightness on
OL,15,FThursday with the odd shower possible
OL,16,Fon Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
